title: Phandom Discord Chat
body:
I’m starting one, because why not! Join if you’re a dan and phil fan who’s looking for friends

description: this is an 18+ chat although there is no age restriction on it. i won’t stop minors from joining, but don’t complain about stuff being inappropriate for your age, kay? also, there are no trigger warnings in this server. this is a say whatever you want chat, if you’re easily triggered or offended, don’t join lmao and if you do and complain later, i won’t have it!

just a nice friendly open for all ages chat. basic rules of healthy social conduct apply. no further restrictions. bring out your inner demon! whether you ship phan or not, whether you write fics, draw art, post shitty memes, looking for everlasting friendships, or do nothing with your life… all are welcome!


just be reasonable kay? the best version of yourself :P


Join using this link: https://discord.gg/826ECtm
